text: Tommy Macias (born 20 January 1993) is a Swedish judoka. He is the 2018 and 2017 European bronze medalist in the 73 kg division. In 2018 he won the Grand Prix in Antalya and Cancun, he also took the bronze in Abu Dhabi Grand Slam and Osaka Grand Slam. In 2017 he took the bronze in IJF Masters St Petersburg and gold in Abu Dhabi Grand Slam. 2019 he won the gold in Ekaterinburg Grand Slam. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Swedish male judoka Category:Living people Category:European Games competitors for Sweden Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games gold medalists for Sweden
